+                          borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(100)),

+                        LineAwesomeIcons.alternate_pencil,

+                        size: 20.0,
+                      ),
+                    ),
+                  )
+                ],
+              ),
+                ],
+              ),
+            ),
+        ));
+  }
+}
